725815f-b.title: Queens: 117th Street - Atlantic Avenue
725815f-b.text:
(1)
117th Street, east side, between Atlantic and 95th
Avenues, showing the Parochial School of St. Benedicts
Roman Catholic Church and the rear of the church. The
church itself is on 118th Street.
P. L. Sperr  May 7, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS
0Vg a 959S
(2)
This is the old church edifice, just below the parochial
achool. Note the steeple of the new church, which is on
118th Street.
P. L. Sperr  May 7, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS
Nleg 2aa5h
